{"tid":947724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海麗邨英國短毛貓失足墮樓亡","createTime":"2018-12-19T13:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T22:33:02.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f0a411355b49773ed722549c9aa832dd7b9d3bcd","tid":947724,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:12:03.000Z","msg":"深水埗海麗邨發生貓隻墮樓案。今日(19日)下午約3時半，有途人行經海信樓對開時，聽到一聲巨響，發現一隻灰色貓隻倒臥在大廈對出空地奄奄一息，隨即報警求助。警方接報到場，為貓隻檢查後，相信貓隻已傷重不治，警方經初步調查後，懷疑貓隻由上址一單位失足墮樓。警方正調查事件及聯絡貓隻主人助查，同時通知相關部門到場檢走貓屍。據悉，墮樓貓隻為英國短毛貓。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181219/bkn-20181219164406313-1219_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181219%2Fbkn-20181219164406313-1219_00822_001.html&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=a81e130f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181219/bkn-20181219164406313-1219_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"c59ce2b5711a3ee8eb3ac396ee12e2e1890b37b7","tid":947724,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多貓跌落街"},{"pid":"8960643e960c4dcb9d002ec6adbc5a98c7b59307","tid":947724,"uid":50740,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:14:43.000Z","msg":"唔裝窗網唔好學人養貓"},{"pid":"58780ac282dac1baec456bdaddf3bdc76388b6a0","tid":947724,"uid":160887,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:15:22.000Z","msg":"屋村撚真係咪撚養貓狗<br />\n<br />\n自己都未養得掂"},{"pid":"a26feea2162098dc0783b756c9fac11a8714af50","tid":947724,"uid":132106,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:15:45.000Z","msg":"24小時求助熱線︰<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線︰23892222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)︰28960000<br />\n生命熱線︰23820000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線︰18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線︰23432255<br />\n醫院管理局精神健康專線(24小時精神健康熱線諮詢服務)：24667350<br />\n明愛向晴熱線：18288"},{"pid":"e4bef42b81edc751bfd219d156a462556e6fd54d","tid":947724,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score